results.title: Penile angioedema developing after 3 years of ACEI therapy.
results.text_hl: All symptoms resolved without complications within 48 h of discontinuing @<m>CHEMICAL_Lisinopril</m> @CHEMICAL_MESH:D017706 @@@lisinopril@@@ and had not recurred at follow-up 4 months later.
